<H1>Customising the <SAMP>less</SAMP> command</H1>

<P>The <STRONG>less</STRONG> command can be given a number of options that
change its behaviour.</P>

<P>These options are used by <A HREF="../environment/index.html">setting the value</A>
of the <SAMP>LESS</SAMP> environment variable.</P>

<P>Options given at the command line override those set by
the environment variable.  An option that is given in the
<SAMP>LESS</SAMP> variable can be reset by starting the command
line option with "<SAMP>-+</SAMP>".</P>

